<li>Donâ€™t miss these upcoming WordCamps:
<ul>
<li><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f1ee-1f1f3.png" alt="ðŸ‡®ðŸ‡³" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://ahmedabad.wordcamp.org/2023/">WordCamp Ahmedabad 2023</a>, India on December 9, 2023</li>



